# WPDAdjuster - Word Processing Document Adjuster

This project follows comprehensive rules defined in the `.cursor/rules/` directory.

## Key Guidelines:
- Offline-capable Python application using PyQt6
- Support for DOCX and RTF document processing
- Modular, minimal, and safe code architecture
- Professional UI with pale color palettes and good contrast
- Comprehensive error handling and validation

## Technology Stack:
- GUI: PyQt6
- DOCX Processing: python-docx
- RTF Processing: pyrtf-ng
- Packaging: PyInstaller

## Rules Reference:
All development rules are defined in `.cursor/rules/` subdirectories:
- Document processing rules
- GUI workflow specifications
- Styling and visual feedback guidelines
- Environment configuration
- Technology stack requirements

Refer to individual rule files for specific implementation details.
